{
  "texts": [
    "Hence, the development of low-cost fine modeling methods for human and fashion items is a significant avenue for future work.",
    "B. Simulation of 3D clothing fabrics Apparel fabric is an essential factor that characterizes the category and style of clothing.",
    "The physical properties of fabrics make clothing with the same style visually different.",
    "For example, a silk shirt is softer than a cotton shirt, and the details of their textures are also different.",
    "Many researchers focus on modeling the texture of clothing materials, and ignore the simulation of the stiffness of the fabrics."
  ]
}